---
title: Persian-Spiced Cauliflower Quinoa Bowl with Sweet Potato and an Avocado Crema
description: Cumin, coriander, and turmeric are a powerhouse trio—they add fragrant, floral, and earthy aromatics to anything they touch. So when they’re used to season veggies, the results are nothing short of a home run. In this recipe, the spices heighten the honey-like flavor of sweet potato, add oomph to mild cauliflower, and turn onion wedges into nuggets of concentrated deliciousness.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/w20-r9-6cf562bb.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/w20-r9-1f337dd0.pdf
servings: 2
course: main course
time required: 35 minutes
cuisine: Fusion
author: HelloFresh
nutrition:
  calories: 630 kcal
  fat: 24 g
  saturated fat: 4.5 g
  carbohydrates: 92 g
  sugar: 17 g
  protein: 16 g
